OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1783792086
OL,3,CTech boss was found with stab wound to
OL,4,Cchest in bathroom, inquest hears
OL,6,FA tech boss whose death sparked a
OL,7,Fmurder investigation was found with a
OL,8,Fstab wound to the chest in a bathroom,
OL,9,Fan inquest has heard.
OL,11,FNeil Muller, 54, died at a house on
OL,12,FLangley Road in the Warwickshire
OL,13,Fvillage of Claverdon on June 7th.
OL,15,FIn a four-minute hearing at Coventry
OL,16,FCoroner's Court on Friday (June 10th),
OL,17,Fcoroner Sean McGovern said Mr Muller,
OL,18,Fwho was the chief executive of Derby-
OL,19,Fbased IT business Node4, suffered a
OL,20,Fcardiac arrest and was pronounced dead
OL,21,Fat 6.37am.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
