PN,34702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1783792086
OL,3,CTech boss was found with stab wound to
OL,4,Cchest in bathroom, inquest hears
OL,6,FPolice were called to attend the scene
OL,7,Fat 6.15am by the ambulance service,
OL,8,Fwho found Mr Muller in a downstairs
OL,9,Fbathroom, just off the kitchen.
OL,11,FHe had suffered a single stab wound to
OL,12,Fthe chest, a superficial cut to the
OL,13,Fwrist, and a weapon was found nearby
OL,14,Fin the sink, the court heard.
OL,16,FA post-mortem examination was carried
OL,17,Fout, and a provisional cause of death,
OL,18,Fsubject to further examination, was a
OL,19,Fstab wound to the chest.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
