FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1783792086
OL,3,CTech boss was found with stab wound to
OL,4,Cchest in bathroom, inquest hears
OL,6,FAt the end of the short hearing, the
OL,7,Fcoroner said: "I open an inquest
OL,8,Ftouching upon the death of Mr Neil
OL,9,FKeith Muller.
OL,11,F"I adjourn the inquest to a date to be
OL,12,Ffixed for police to provide evidence
OL,13,Fand for (the pathologist) to provide
OL,14,Fhis final report."
OL,16,FLess than an hour after Mr Muller was
OL,17,Fpronounced dead, a 55-year-old woman
OL,18,Ffrom Birmingham was arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,26,@oD@OOUsD@AOUvD@RO]
