CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1783792086
OL,3,CTech boss was found with stab wound to
OL,4,Cchest in bathroom, inquest hears
OL,6,FShe was later bailed, Warwickshire
OL,7,FPolice said.
OL,9,FIn a statement released after his
OL,10,Fdeath, a spokesman for Node4 said: "We
OL,11,Fare absolutely devastated by the death
OL,12,Fof our CEO Neil Muller.
OL,14,F"Although Neil only recently joined
OL,15,FNode4, he made a meaningful impact in
OL,16,Fa short space of time.
OL,18,F"He brought real energy, momentum, and
OL,19,Fpassion to the business, and his loss
OL,20,Fwill be deeply felt by people across
OL,21,FNode4 and the wider industry.
OL,26,@rD@dOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
